"   (For additional information",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?40/10/41124?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Atovaquone and proguanil: Patient drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   and",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_pediatric\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/58/19365?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Atovaquone and proguanil: Pediatric drug information\"",
"   </a>",
